data.description:
Welcome to this exceptional 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom residence situated on a 1.5-acre lot, now featuring the added benefit of solar panels. With a total of 3,388 square feet of living space, this home not only offers a wealth of desirable features but also incorporates sustainable energy solutions to reduce your environmental impact and save on energy costs.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious open kitchen with a center island, perfect for preparing delicious meals while enjoying the natural light that streams in through the energy-efficient windows. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and a convenient walk-in pantry, providing ample storage space for all your culinary needs.

Adjacent to the kitchen, the living area features a cozy fireplace, offering warmth and charm for those chilly evenings. Imagine relaxing with family and friends in this inviting space, knowing that your home is powered, in part, by clean and renewable solar energy.

The primary bedroom of this home is a sanctuary of comfort and relaxation. With its spacious layout and a walk-through shower, you can indulge in a luxurious bathing experience while being mindful of your energy consumption. The integration of solar panels ensures that you can enjoy the modern conveniences you desire while minimizing your carbon footprint.

The thoughtful design of this home places all the rooms on the main level, ensuring easy accessibility and a seamless flow throughout. The combination of hardwood floors and carpeting adds a touch of elegance and comfort to the living spaces.

In addition to the impressive solar panel installation, this two-story home offers a large bonus room, allowing for versatile usage and customization according to your specific needs. Embrace the opportunity to create a home office, recreational area, or home theater that perfectly suits your lifestyle.

Outside, the 1.5-acre lot offers ample space for outdoor activities and the potential for further sustainability initiatives. The solar panels not only contribute to reducing your carbon footprint but also provide the opportunity for energy savings that can benefit both your wallet and the environment.

Don't miss the chance to own this remarkable home with the added advantage of solar panels. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and sustainable living. Contact me today to arrange a viewing and witness the incredible features and benefits of this exceptional property firsthand.

The home comes with all appliances, Refrigerator
and washer & dryer. Lifetime Warranty on the solar panels.
